{"tid":2180042,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳 Google 台灣 53 億建新數據中心   外媒：應對國安法或遷港服務","createTime":"2020-08-29T14:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T13:55:47.000Z","uid":51620,"like":108,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"cd7542f552612e9cafbafcda132cf034b554167b","tid":2180042,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T14:26:13.000Z","msg":"有傳 Google 購買中國人造纖維（中纖）在台灣雲林縣斗六市 20 公頃的土地，用作興建台灣第三座資料中心。業內人士預計相關投資金額至少新台幣 200 億元（約港幣 53 億元）。有外媒分析認為 Google 此舉是應對《港區國安法》，計劃將服務中心移離香港遷往亞洲鄰近地區，但 Google  在 26 日低調回應事件稱，不會對報導作出評論。<br />\n<br />\n雲林縣政府建設處處長李俊興回應傳媒查詢時表示，中纖確實於上週公告出售 20 公頃土地，但買賣雙方尚未提出土地擁有權轉移申請，無從得知是否為 Google 所購買。<br />\n<br />\n中纖上週公告出售位於雲林縣斗六市的六塊土地，交易總額為新台幣 36.44 億元（約港幣 9.6 億元），交易對象為 BECKETT ENTERPRISES 公司；經向斗六地政查詢，因雙方未有進行產權移轉，無法確認是否為 Google 所購買。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/08/29/taiwan-google/life-tech/?fbclid=IwAR3XH2qJoKTeT9pwJw1Y8DIWP9a0Fh7h1ou5uKxpbbvjKIpRGznFRChcMHU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F08%2F29%2Ftaiwan-google%2Flife-tech%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3XH2qJoKTeT9pwJw1Y8DIWP9a0Fh7h1ou5uKxpbbvjKIpRGznFRChcMHU&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLMeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=6945ec82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/08/29/taiwan-google/life-tech/?fbclid=IwAR3XH2qJoKTeT9pwJw1Y8DIWP9a0Fh7h1ou5uKxpbbvjKIpRGznFRChcMHU</a>"},{"pid":"793e50301abd5eb0908280ca0e4b85c6bd805813","tid":2180042,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T14:28:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69af4dc2210e8b89ebbac7a2cbf1cd243599fa20","tid":2180042,"uid":138868,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T14:29:46.000Z","msg":"國安法為香港創科帶來機遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127369a398fbf0df7dc3760